Package: touchosc2midi
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, pyliblo3
Description: TouchOSC to MIDI bridge
 Bridges TouchOSC (iOS/Android) OSC messages to ALSA/JACK MIDI.
 Installed in an isolated venv at /opt/pistomp/venvs/touchosc2midi.
